                &kp LSHFT   &kp LALT    &kp LCTRL   &kp LGUI    &kp C_VOL_UP    &trans      PTAB        &kp LEFT    &kp RIGHT   NTAB
    &trans      &kp C_PREV  &kp C_MUTE  &kp C_PP    &kp C_NEXT  &kp C_VOL_DN    &trans      &kp HOME    &kp PG_UP   &kp PG_DN   &kp END     &trans
